        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" data-event="cta_click" data-lead-type="request_inspection">Request Inspection</a>
        <p class="muted" style="font-size:0.78rem;margin-top:14px;">By contacting us you agree we may follow up by phone, text, or email about your inquiry. Message and data rates may apply. Reply STOP to opt out at any time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <div>&copy; {year} Smart Termite Tulsa. All rights reserved.</div>
      <div>Local visibility support by <a href="https://myusalocal.com">MyUSA Local</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
